  "description": "<p><strong>Class 3A Wheelchair Transport Driver (Day & Night Shifts Available)</strong><br />We have new vehicles coming in and are hiring <strong>one day-shift driver</strong> and <strong>one night-shift driver</strong>. Bonus available.</p><p><strong>Salary:</strong> SGD <strong>$3,000 – $3,300</strong> + Overtime Pay (OT paid separately)<br /><strong>Working Days:</strong> Monday to Saturday<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 06:00–18:00 (night shift also available)</p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Valid <strong>Class 3 Singapore Driving Licence</strong></p></li><li><p>Familiar with Singapore routes</p></li><li><p>Hardworking and responsible</p></li><li><p>Good service attitude</p></li><li><p>Must be able to commit to <strong>regular overtime</strong></p></li><li><p>Main duties include transporting government dialysis patients, airport arrivals for tourists, and charter services</p></li></ul>",
